<h3>Generator Options</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code>--stimulus</code>: Generates a new Stimulus controller named <code>card_controller.js</code> and registers it for enhanced interactivity</li>
  <li><code>--directory</code>: Customize the component location (defaults to <code>app/views/rui/components</code>)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Component Properties</h3>
<ul>
  <li><code>title</code>: The main heading of the card (String, optional)</li>
  <li><code>content</code>: Body content for the card:
    <ul>
      <li>Can be a String or HTML-safe content</li>
      <li>When present, renders in a <code>prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert mt-2 mb-4</code> wrapper div</li>
      <li>When passing a block, it renders content directly ignoring <code>content</code> argument.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><code>actions</code>: Slot for buttons, links, or other interactive elements:
    <ul>
      <li>Accepts HTML-safe content</li>
      <li>Optional - typically used for buttons or action links</li>
      <li>Renders at the bottom of the card when present</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><code>classes</code>: Additional Tailwind CSS classes for custom styling:
    <ul>
      <li>Applied to the main card wrapper div</li>
      <li>Useful for spacing, sizing, or color modifications</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3>Notes</h3>
<ul>
  <li>The card uses a clean, modern design with rounded corners and subtle borders</li>
  <li>Includes built-in dark mode support with appropriate color variants</li>
  <li>The title is styled as an <code>h3</code> element with <code>h4</code> class for consistent typography</li>
  <li>Content and actions are conditionally rendered only when present</li>
  <li>Uses semantic HTML structure for better accessibility</li>
  <li>Default styling includes white background, padding, and border with dark mode variants</li>
</ul>

